{
  "texts": [
    "FCNN also has filters in decision making layers.",
    "Fast-RCNNFast-RCNN was introduced in 2015 by [109].",
    "Fast-RCNN is used for faster object detection.",
    "Its architecture is pretty much similar to the RCNN but in Fast-RCNN we direct give input image to convolutional neural network to generate a convolutional feature map.",
    "The reason that the fast-RCNN is faster than the RCNN is that there is no need to give input a lot of region proposals to CNN every time."
  ]
}